00:11:41,909 --> 00:11:46,163
<c.bg_transparent>Aku adiknya, Alphonse Elric.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Senang bertemu denganmu.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:11:46,247 --> 00:11:48,749
<c.bg_transparent>Aku Ling Yao.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Senang bertemu dengan kalian.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:11:49,291 --> 00:11:53,546
<c.bg_transparent>LIng, ceritakan lebih banyak</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tentang alkahestry ini.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:11:53,963 --> 00:11:57,383
<c.bg_transparent>Tidak bisa. Aku bukan ahli alkahestry.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:11:59,135 --> 00:12:03,180
<c.bg_transparent>Jika kau bukan ahli alkahestry,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mengapa kau datang untuk mencari tahu?</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:12:03,681 --> 00:12:05,057
<c.bg_transparent>Aku sedang mencari sesuatu.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:12:05,891 --> 00:12:08,477
<c.bg_transparent>Mungkin kalian mengetahuinya.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:12:09,895 --> 00:12:10,813
<c.bg_transparent>Batu Bertuah.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:12:12,565 --> 00:12:14,316
<c.bg_transparent>Aku sangat menginginkannya.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:12:15,317 --> 00:12:17,528
<c.bg_transparent>Apa kalian mengetahui sesuatu</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tentang batu itu?</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:12:19,363 --> 00:12:21,449
<c.bg_transparent>Kami tidak tahu.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:12:23,075 --> 00:12:24,618
<c.bg_transparent>Menurutku, kalian mengetahuinya.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:12:27,913 --> 00:12:29,540
<c.bg_transparent>Apa kalian bisa menceritakannya?</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:12:30,833 --> 00:12:32,418
<c.bg_transparent>Untuk apa Batu Bertuah itu?</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:12:35,629 --> 00:12:38,966
<c.bg_transparent>Aku ingin menjadi abadi.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:12:42,636 --> 00:12:44,764
<c.bg_transparent>Jadi, bisakah kalian memberitahuku?</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:12:44,847 --> 00:12:47,892
<c.bg_transparent>Keabadian. Itu omong kosong.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:12:47,975 --> 00:12:49,560
<c.bg_transparent>Aku serius.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:12:49,643 --> 00:12:53,063
<c.bg_transparent>Beginikah sikapmu saat meminta tolong?</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:12:54,106 --> 00:12:55,149
<c.bg_transparent>Sepertinya tidak!</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:12:59,153 --> 00:13:00,821
<c.bg_transparent>Kakak!</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:13:00,905 --> 00:13:03,657
<c.bg_transparent>- Kalian akan menantang kami?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Tunggu dulu!</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:13:09,205 --> 00:13:11,707
<c.bg_transparent>Dasar berengsek.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Siapa kalian, ahli akrobat?</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:13:11,791 --> 00:13:14,919
<c.bg_transparent>Mungkin ini gaya bertarung Xing.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Sangat menantang.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:13:15,002 --> 00:13:17,213
<c.bg_transparent>- Meskipun begitu...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Ya.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:13:17,588 --> 00:13:19,965
<c.bg_transparent>- Mereka tak sekuat...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Guru!</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:13:23,803 --> 00:13:25,054
<c.bg_transparent>Ada apa ini?</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:13:28,349 --> 00:13:29,975
<c.bg_transparent>Mereka pergi.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:13:31,977 --> 00:13:33,979
<c.bg_transparent>- Aku pesan hidangan penutup.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Baik.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:14:00,589 --> 00:14:01,507
<c.bg_transparent>Astaga.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:14:08,848 --> 00:14:10,057
<c.bg_transparent>Sial.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:14:10,140 --> 00:14:12,935
<c.bg_transparent>Membicarakan Batu Bertuah dan keabadian,</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:14:13,018 --> 00:14:15,312
<c.bg_transparent>lalu menyerang kami secara tiba-tiba!</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:14:15,396 --> 00:14:19,650
<c.bg_transparent>Apa tujuan kalian dan si Bodoh</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>yang suka memejamkan mata itu?</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:14:24,029 --> 00:14:26,198
<c.bg_transparent>Aku mengenainya. Aduh!</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:14:29,785 --> 00:14:31,245
<c.bg_transparent>Aduh...</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:14:33,163 --> 00:14:37,835
<c.bg_transparent><i>Begitu aku menyebutnya,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>"si Bodoh yang suka memejamkan mata"...</i></c.bg_transparent>

177
00:14:38,836 --> 00:14:40,546
<c.bg_transparent><i>Aku mengerti.</i></c.bg_transparent>

178
00:14:42,756 --> 00:14:44,842
<c.bg_transparent>Lama tak bertemu, Paninya!</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:14:44,925 --> 00:14:46,927
<c.bg_transparent>Sedang apa kau?</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:14:47,011 --> 00:14:49,305
<c.bg_transparent>Aku punya ide yang sangat bagus.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:14:49,388 --> 00:14:52,308
<c.bg_transparent>Paninya, aku membutuhkan bantuanmu.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:14:52,808 --> 00:14:55,895
<c.bg_transparent><i>Aneh, aku tak merasakan adanya energi</i></c.bg_transparent>

183
00:14:55,978 --> 00:14:58,689
<c.bg_transparent><i>dari orang hidup</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>yang ada di baju zirah itu.</i></c.bg_transparent>

184
00:14:58,772 --> 00:15:00,566
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sebenarnya, siapa dia?</i></c.bg_transparent>

185
00:15:03,152 --> 00:15:06,405
<c.bg_transparent>Apa menurutmu temanmu bisa membantu?</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:15:06,488 --> 00:15:08,073
<c.bg_transparent>Dasar bodoh!</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:15:12,036 --> 00:15:15,205
<c.bg_transparent>Ada apa? Aku mulai bisa menebak gerakanmu!</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:15:18,125 --> 00:15:19,460
<c.bg_transparent>Jika ini upaya terbaikmu,</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:15:19,877 --> 00:15:22,922
<c.bg_transparent>Ling si Berengsek itu</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>pasti juga tak ada apa-apanya!</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:15:27,551 --> 00:15:32,681
<c.bg_transparent><i>Begitu aku menghina tuannya,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>dia kehilangan kendali.</i></c.bg_transparent>

191
00:15:32,765 --> 00:15:33,891
<c.bg_transparent><i>Saat itu terjadi,</i></c.bg_transparent>

192
00:15:35,768 --> 00:15:38,145
<c.bg_transparent>serangannya menjadi kacau dan berlebihan!</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:15:41,649 --> 00:15:43,734
<c.bg_transparent>Sepertinya, inilah waktunya</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:15:45,194 --> 00:15:47,029
<c.bg_transparent>untuk melihat wajahmu!</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:15:48,447 --> 00:15:49,406
<c.bg_transparent>Perempuan?</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:16:01,919 --> 00:16:03,879
<c.bg_transparent><i>Meriam di tungkai prostetiknya?</i></c.bg_transparent>

197
00:16:03,963 --> 00:16:05,589
<c.bg_transparent><i>Negeri ini tak bisa dianggap remeh.</i></c.bg_transparent>

198
00:16:07,675 --> 00:16:09,009
<c.bg_transparent>Apa?</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:16:14,807 --> 00:16:17,142
<c.bg_transparent>Sepertinya inilah yang kau harapkan.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:16:17,226 --> 00:16:20,062
<c.bg_transparent>Alkahestry, tanpa peranti?</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:16:20,938 --> 00:16:24,316
<c.bg_transparent>Apakah kakakku baik-baik saja?</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:16:29,655 --> 00:16:30,823
<c.bg_transparent>Aku terlalu berlebihan.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:16:32,491 --> 00:16:35,244
<c.bg_transparent>Bagaimana ini?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Master Ling pasti akan memarahiku.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:16:42,126 --> 00:16:43,335
<c.bg_transparent>Hei, Anak Perempuan.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:16:44,753 --> 00:16:47,297
<c.bg_transparent>Mengapa kau menggunakan granat</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>di tengah kota?</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:16:47,381 --> 00:16:49,008
<c.bg_transparent>Kau bisa memakan korban.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:16:49,550 --> 00:16:51,927
<c.bg_transparent>Kau melepaskan tanganmu?</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:16:52,469 --> 00:16:55,514
<c.bg_transparent>Aku sering mengejar kelinci</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>saat masih kecil.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:16:55,597 --> 00:16:57,808
<c.bg_transparent>Jadi, membuat perangkap</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sangatlah mudah bagiku.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:16:57,891 --> 00:16:59,435
<c.bg_transparent>Kakak!</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:16:59,852 --> 00:17:01,186
<c.bg_transparent>Hei, Al!</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:17:01,270 --> 00:17:02,980
<c.bg_transparent>Kerja bagus, Semuanya.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:17:03,063 --> 00:17:05,524
<c.bg_transparent>Mengapa kau bisa begitu riang?</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:17:05,607 --> 00:17:08,277
<c.bg_transparent>Kalian sangat hebat.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:17:08,360 --> 00:17:11,780
<c.bg_transparent>Bagaimana jika kalian bekerja untukku</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dan kita taklukkan negeri ini?</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:17:11,864 --> 00:17:15,492
<c.bg_transparent>Hentikan ocehanmu itu!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Kembalilah ke Xing sekarang.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:17:15,576 --> 00:17:16,910
<c.bg_transparent>Rupanya kalian di sana!</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:17:17,703 --> 00:17:21,165
<c.bg_transparent>Kalian yang telah menghancurkan kota,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>bukan?</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:17:21,248 --> 00:17:24,168
<c.bg_transparent>- Kalian harus membayar kerusakannya.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Juga tagihan makannya.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:17:24,251 --> 00:17:26,253
<c.bg_transparent>Tunggu sebentar.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:17:26,336 --> 00:17:29,006
<c.bg_transparent>Tangkap dan minta mereka</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>untuk membayar semuanya.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:17:29,298 --> 00:17:33,927
<c.bg_transparent>Aku tak mengerti bahasa</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>yang kalian gunakan. Dah!</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:17:34,011 --> 00:17:35,846
<c.bg_transparent>Hei, tunggu!</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:17:36,597 --> 00:17:39,058
<c.bg_transparent>Apa? Astaga, dia kabur!</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:17:40,184 --> 00:17:41,310
<c.bg_transparent>Dia juga!</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:17:41,977 --> 00:17:46,857
<c.bg_transparent>Astaga, bagaimana caraku memperbaikinya</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>jika kondisiku seperti ini?</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:50,444
<c.bg_transparent>Tak apa-apa, Kak.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Biar aku saja yang melakukannya.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:17:52,362 --> 00:17:55,282
<c.bg_transparent>Kau bisa melakukannya</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tanpa lingkaran transmutasi?</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:17:55,365 --> 00:17:58,535
<c.bg_transparent>Itu karena memoriku tentang kebenaran</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>telah kembali.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:18:00,829 --> 00:18:01,747
<c.bg_transparent>Artinya...</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:03,123
<c.bg_transparent>TEKNIK ALKIMIA</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>MARTABAT KAKAK</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:18:03,207 --> 00:18:04,500
<c.bg_transparent>TINGGI</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:18:07,044 --> 00:18:08,212
<c.bg_transparent>MARTABAT KAKAK</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:18:08,629 --> 00:18:11,048
<c.bg_transparent>Serahkan sisanya kepadaku.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:18:12,424 --> 00:18:14,134
<c.bg_transparent>Ada apa, Kakak?</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:18:15,719 --> 00:18:17,012
<c.bg_transparent>Kami kembali!</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:18:17,638 --> 00:18:19,056
<c.bg_transparent>Hei, kita bertemu lagi.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:18:21,433 --> 00:18:23,769
<c.bg_transparent>Jangan hanya duduk dan minum teh saja!</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:18:23,894 --> 00:18:26,105
<c.bg_transparent>Mengapa kau jahat sekali?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Kita ini teman.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:18:26,188 --> 00:18:31,110
<c.bg_transparent>Siapa yang kau panggil "teman"?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Kedua temanmu menyusahkan kami.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:18:31,193 --> 00:18:33,779
<c.bg_transparent>Lupakan saja.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Aku yang akan bicara dengan mereka.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:18:34,988 --> 00:18:37,950
<c.bg_transparent>Anak perempuan itu bernama Lan Fan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dan pria tua itu bernama Fu.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:18:38,700 --> 00:18:40,285
<c.bg_transparent>Mereka melayani kami</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:18:40,369 --> 00:18:42,746
<c.bg_transparent>selama beberapa generasi,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>maka maafkan mereka.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:18:43,080 --> 00:18:46,542
<c.bg_transparent>Untuk seseorang yang memanipulasi</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>demi mendapatkan makanan,</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:18:46,625 --> 00:18:48,919
<c.bg_transparent>statusmu pasti tinggi</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>karena memiliki dua pembantu.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:18:49,002 --> 00:18:52,005
<c.bg_transparent>Sebenarnya, aku adalah putra kaisar.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:18:52,297 --> 00:18:54,508
<c.bg_transparent>Apa? Putra kaisar?</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:18:57,928 --> 00:18:59,513
<c.bg_transparent>Maksudmu, kau adalah...</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:18:59,596 --> 00:19:01,306
<c.bg_transparent>Pangeran?</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:19:03,725 --> 00:19:06,937
<c.bg_transparent>Biasanya orang-orang akan terkejut</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>setelah mendengarnya.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:19:07,020 --> 00:19:09,231
<c.bg_transparent>Maaf. Hanya saja, ini sangat tak terduga.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:19:09,314 --> 00:19:11,483
<c.bg_transparent>Bayangkan saja, ada pangeran yang terkapar</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:19:11,567 --> 00:19:13,443
<c.bg_transparent>di jalan dan meminta makanan gratis.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:19:16,947 --> 00:19:19,366
<c.bg_transparent>Aku takkan membiarkan kalian</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>menghina Master.</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:19:20,701 --> 00:19:21,618
<c.bg_transparent>Kau di sini?</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:19:22,035 --> 00:19:24,872
<c.bg_transparent>Mungkin itu memang</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sama sekali tak mengejutkan.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:19:25,330 --> 00:19:27,624
<c.bg_transparent>Kaisar memiliki banyak anak.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:19:28,834 --> 00:19:33,213
<c.bg_transparent>Xing adalah negeri yang dibangun</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dari 50 klan berbeda</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:19:33,297 --> 00:19:36,300
<c.bg_transparent>yang dipimpin oleh seorang kaisar.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:19:36,383 --> 00:19:39,720
<c.bg_transparent>Putri dari setiap pemimpin klan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dinikahkan dengan kaisar,</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:19:39,803 --> 00:19:41,305
<c.bg_transparent>dan mengandung anak-anak kaisar.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:19:42,097 --> 00:19:47,686
<c.bg_transparent>Kaisar yang sekarang memiliki</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>24 putra dan 19 putri.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:19:47,769 --> 00:19:49,730
<c.bg_transparent>Aku anak ke-12.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:19:50,063 --> 00:19:52,566
<c.bg_transparent>Ada 43 anak...</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:19:52,649 --> 00:19:55,194
<c.bg_transparent>Apakah ada kompetisi</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>untuk menjadi penerusnya?</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:19:55,277 --> 00:19:58,113
<c.bg_transparent>Ya, itulah masalah</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>yang tengah kami hadapi.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:19:58,989 --> 00:20:02,075
<c.bg_transparent>Kesehatan kaisar makin menurun.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:20:02,159 --> 00:20:06,038
<c.bg_transparent>Tiap klan akan mencari muka</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>di depan kaisar.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:20:06,121 --> 00:20:07,247
<c.bg_transparent>Begitu pun denganku.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:20:07,664 --> 00:20:11,043
<c.bg_transparent>Kau menginginkan keabadian</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>untuk menarik perhatiannya.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:20:11,126 --> 00:20:12,127
<c.bg_transparent>Benar.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:20:12,419 --> 00:20:16,256
<c.bg_transparent>Jadi, berikan aku informasi</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mengenai Batu Bertuah itu.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:20:16,715 --> 00:20:20,427
<c.bg_transparent>Tidak. Batu Bertuah bukanlah alat</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>yang bisa kau gunakan!</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:20:21,386 --> 00:20:23,597
<c.bg_transparent>Cepat katakan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>atau aku akan selalu mengikutimu.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:20:23,680 --> 00:20:24,806
<c.bg_transparent>Jangan lakukan itu!</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:20:24,890 --> 00:20:26,475
<c.bg_transparent>Aku pulang!</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:20:26,808 --> 00:20:29,811
<c.bg_transparent>Sepertinya ada keributan besar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>di tengah kota,</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:20:29,895 --> 00:20:31,480
<c.bg_transparent>maka butuh waktu...</c.bg_transparent>

